{"tid":492209,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【修改議規】梁君彥：我的裁決是不容辯論","createTime":"2017-12-07T10:09:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-07T10:58:49.000Z","uid":70985,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"2dc49c7c192c9485a32505830e775826ed180e1d","tid":492209,"uid":70985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T10:09:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20171207/s00001/d6b9729d95e4ce994c3d0256e971c960.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20171207%2Fs00001%2Fd6b9729d95e4ce994c3d0256e971c960.jpg&h=fb737853&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n立法會通過《實習律師修訂規則》中止待續議案後，隨即進入審議修改《議事規則》議程。民主派質疑主席梁君彥裁決，又期望容許議員發言時間多於15分鐘。梁君彥則重申，「我的裁決是不容辯論」，又指「我現在用時間解釋（裁決理由），其實我是不需要解釋的」。<br />\n<br />\n立法會10時許準備進入審議修改《議事規則》議程，但民主派議員希望容許議員發言時間多於15分鐘。梁君彥重申，其裁決符合《基本法》、《議事規則》及過往處理方法，明言「我已就有關事作出裁決，希望議員不要在議會上辯論我的裁決，我覺得我的做法符合議事規則」。<br />\n他又說，「如果分開辯論，議員有無限力量，今年整年都不可以完成所有的&hellip;&hellip;」話未說完，有議員在座位大叫「梁君彥黑哨可恥」。<br />\n梁君彥之後強調，「我的裁決是不容辯論。我現在用時間解釋，其實我是不需要解釋的」，呼籲議員留意「我的裁決已經做了」。<br />\n公民黨楊岳橋再期望梁君彥，以「例外情況」考慮，容許議員發言多於15分鐘。香港本土毛孟靜則認為，議案涉及「個人利益及角色衝突」，因主席權力會無限充權，故「個人利益嫌疑一定要避開」。<br />\n<br />\n不過梁君彥指，「我作為主席沒有利益衝突，可以繼續主持會議」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171207/s00001/1512615803922\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171207%2Fs00001%2F1512615803922&d=RAgTfSvKuYoXmTgMV7u6nqS6uTmBE%2FuUnOR61Sj848o%3D&h=a4dbf5c6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171207%2Fs00001%2F1512615803922&h=eba3bd0e\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171207/s00001/1512615803922</a>"},{"pid":"2b8c6df2f9084dbe0887c835b5a0c48862e400be","tid":492209,"uid":70985,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T10:10:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://news.memehk.com/img/post/12302_2015-11-27_093346.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.memehk.com%2Fimg%2Fpost%2F12302_2015-11-27_093346.jpg&h=955e97f3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6d5c693b57364420d57a6c37bfc532a4f5c7fef7","tid":492209,"uid":156652,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T10:10:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/07/181038_10dcf45bd3bd1c3cc4d5a98e596a066f.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F07%2F181038_10dcf45bd3bd1c3cc4d5a98e596a066f.gif&h=3e497249&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"56bbcc414836e47dfa7085ad374cb4f356db63f9","tid":492209,"uid":21917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T10:18:16.000Z","msg":"你仲惡過共產黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"628813d281a7eca956ec0f6c4ba3a55cd499b2e9","tid":492209,"uid":32577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T10:57:54.000Z","msg":"超越習大大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26eb116008a512506844af833c35e040250fbbab","tid":492209,"uid":71524,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T10:58:49.000Z","msg":"屌你老味<br />\n真係仆街冚家剷<br />\n咁撚多人死唔見你死"}]}